The Beautiful Suwannee River
A relaxing place to stay.
We are directly off Hwy 19 on your way to the many beautiful getaways Florida has to offer. You will find 40 full hookup campsites that are big rig friendly. Our amenities include Wi-Fi, pet-friendly environments, dump station, swimming pool, picnic tables, restrooms with hot showers and laundry facilities.
